# Chicken Tikka Biryani Bowl

Based on [https://www.easypeasyfoodie.com/chicken-tikka-biryani/](https://www.easypeasyfoodie.com/chicken-tikka-biryani) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251116030023/https://www.easypeasyfoodie.com/chicken-tikka-biryani/)) and [https://butfirstchai.com/chicken-tikka-biryani/](https://butfirstchai.com/chicken-tikka-biryani) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251220044801/https://butfirstchai.com/chicken-tikka-biryani/))

